Summary: jeho-diary: lots of changes
Keywords: 

* jeho-diary.el: fixed some incorrect defcustom groups
(jeho-diary-calendar-show): new variable
(jeho-diary-day-page-face, jeho-diary-diary-face, jeho-diary-block-face) 
(jeho-diary-anniversary-face): new facesxb
(jeho-diary-entry-handler-alist): new variable: handlers for diary sexps
(jeho-diary-entry-calendar-face-alist): new variable: faces for
particular diary sexps
(jeho-diary-carry-tasks-forward): new convenience function 
(jeho-diary-add-to-date-planner): new convenience function 
(jeho-diary-cyclic-entry-sexp): added this to the cyclic entry data
structure 
(jeho-diary-native-date, jeho-diary-native-text, jeho-diary-native-sexp):
functions to access diary data structure
(jeho-diary-format-anniversary, jeho-diary-format-block): handlers for
diary sexps
(jeho-diary-make-entry-element): added handling
(jeho-diary-get-cyclic): now gets information for carried forward task
handling 
(jeho-diary-get-date-range): reverses the list now, so that it is in date
order 
(jeho-diary-restore-carried-forward-diary-entries): deal with carried
forward entries
(plan): advise plan to deal with carriedforward entries
(jeho-diary-schedule-sort): fixed sorting the schedule
(jeho-diary-do-plan-marking, jeho-diary-do-diary-marking): deal with
these differently rather than the old off-the-peg function
(jeho-diary-goto, jeho-diary-calendar-insinuate): standalone calendar
functionality [no longer piggy-backs on planner.el]

